title: The Who - The Who By Numbers [2011 Remaster] [320k MP3]
description:
The Who by Numbers is the seventh album by English rock band The Who, released on 3 October 1975 in the United Kingdom through Polydor Records, and on 25 October 1975 in the United States by MCA Records. On 24 December 2011 the album was remastered and reissued in Japan using the original mix of the album. The live bonus tracks from the previous edition were included on the reissue. The packaging replicates the original vinyl release of the album.
